# Server-side only (Vercel env, NOT bundled into client)
# EVE_EYES_API_KEY=eve_ak_YOUR_KEY_HERE
#
# In dev mode, Vite proxy forwards to eve-eyes.d0v.xyz (see vite.config.ts).
# In production, Vercel serverless function at /api/eve-eyes/* handles auth.
# Set EVE_EYES_API_KEY in Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables.
